"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, I have an update on my market garden. And if you've been following my uh shorts at all, you'll know that I am looking to take my backyard garden to market and monetize my hobby, but also kind of create an income from things I'd be doing anyway. I have an excess. I grow too much, so why not sell it? Why not incentivize it? I want to document through this process. And this past weekend I talked with Tim and Leanne of the Memorial Villages Farmers Market. I've been selling fermented foods through them and with them for about five or six years. And now I have transitioned over to market garden. I talked to them just this past weekend about getting back in there. I've been out for about three, four months, and uh they said they would accommodate me. And uh so in about three weeks, hopefully that's about when my tomatoes will be really coming in proper. I'll be in the farmer's market. I'm officially doing it, there's no turning back now. If this goes and I fall flat on my face, at least I'll be documenting it so everybody can see it. Anyway, thanks y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, I have an update on my market garden.\",\n      \"start\": 0.88,\n      \"end\": 5.04,\n      \"duration\": 4.16,\n      \"confidence\": 0.99,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.991\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 1.12,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.44,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.44,\n          \"end\": 1.76,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n     